{"tid":1429451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[官方]聽日有民間記者會","createTime":"2019-08-07T13:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T03:24:49.000Z","uid":301497,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"12cb09e861327a0cc0d0b5140fb7d622ce487f68","tid":1429451,"uid":301497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"第二次的民間記者會主題為：「踐踏法治 警暴濫權 以謊言和子彈治港」。團隊是次邀請到4位市民，分別有運動中擔任救護員身份、普通家庭主婦、集會工作人員等，上來分享相關經驗。團隊希望能借是次機會，提供多角度意見，還原事實真相，從而指出及指證警方及政府過去的謊言。<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年8月8日<br />\n時間：14：00<br />\n<br />\n直播：<br />\n基進報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/radicalhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fradicalhk%2F&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLHO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=44cd607a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/radicalhk/</a><br />\n<br />\nTG Channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/citizenspresscon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcitizenspresscon&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLHO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=f76fcd2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/citizenspresscon</a>"},{"pid":"26fc6f609daa5f51fb5fe33461a55dd2b5462ce3","tid":1429451,"uid":74058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我要見記者"},{"pid":"6ca02eca23066aa772c2c3d694eac536feb4dfdb","tid":1429451,"uid":83476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:40:06.000Z","msg":"［突發］第二次民間記者會傳媒邀請函<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1428756/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1428756/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎梁振英同志大駕光臨連登<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1429236/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1429236/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"eaa25d7755ced1c201157b58114397ff3ffe10e0","tid":1429451,"uid":298433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-0